https://www.howtographql.com/typescript-apollo/0-introduction/

Install the necessary packages along with their type definitions:

npm install apollo-server@^ graphql@^ nexus@^


Setting up Nexus
npx ts-node --transpile-only src/schema


npm i pg@8.2.1

npm install prisma@ --save-dev
npm install @prisma/client@


npx prisma migrate dev --name "init"



npx prisma generate

npx ts-node src/script.ts

npm run generate  /// updates schema .graphql and nexus-typegen.ts
